{
 "name": "RPlog_Return_Home",
 "title": "Return Home",
 "summary": "The Jedi Jessalyn Valios and the mechanic Orson journey to a long-abandoned colony on Yavin 4, some 1200 kilometers from the great Massassi Temple, where neglect has let the jungle overgrow the makeshift shelters. Returning to this overgrown place steeped in memory, the two reflect on the past and what the ruined settlement means to them. The quiet, contemplative scene traces a homecoming to a forgotten corner of Yavin 4 and the bond between Jessalyn and Orson.",
